{"tid":319328,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《蜘蛛俠強勢回歸》：令人困倦的又又又回歸","createTime":"2017-07-12T16:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T05:59:45.000Z","uid":14730,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af1fa5a797d4f719c25aef0d5a158c4418d36f8c","tid":319328,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:51:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/13/005044_3974f308cb0fe7afca2f1e900a3fbaa7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F13%2F005044_3974f308cb0fe7afca2f1e900a3fbaa7.jpg&h=98f1a3d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從來都很喜歡蜘蛛俠，因為他夠平易近人，既沒有蝙蝠俠的雄厚家財，也沒有Iron Man的發明實力。蜘蛛俠只是普通不過的紐約少年Peter Parker，一邊上學一邊為報紙影相賺外快。02年的《蜘蛛俠》，Tobey Maguire演活了蜘蛛俠的正直及單純，和女神Kirsten Dunst的鹿撞初戀也令人難忘。如是者拍了三集，之後系列換走導演Sam Raimi兼Tobey Maguire，由《心跳500天》的Marc Webb掌舵，或者是先入為主觀感使然，只覺Andrew Garfield加Emma Stone配搭奇怪，Andrew Garfield夠青春，但卻沒有蜘蛛俠應有的傻氣，戲名叫《The Amazing Spider Man》，但可惜劇情一點也不amazing。<br />\n<br />\n「Amazing」兩集之後又過三年，想不到的是蜘蛛俠這次索性叫「homecoming」，新進導演Jon Watts找來比Tobey Maguire和Andrew Garfield當年演蜘蛛俠時更年輕的Tom Holland，由一臉稚氣的他來演仍然在學的Peter Parker，論年齡是最合適的。或許Marvel也知再講他怎樣發現自己擁有異能已太例牌，叔叔嬸嬸被害也已人所共知，因此這次索性找Iron Man來crossover，Peter小子在已是熟男的Iron Man前其實更像是Spider Boy，Iron Man索性當上他的導師，讓他在superhero聯盟中當實習生。一老一嫩的odd couple組合無疑有新鮮感，Tom Holland作為青澀少年，演出也夠自然流暢。只是當Marvel年年「曬冷」，幾乎每部戲都要齊齊整整全家福出動拜年時，作為觀眾的我除了講句好熟口面好親切外，難免有點疲倦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2t4uwA5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2t4uwA5&d=2OlQ0AFCd%2FcchBQ1Rtj%2BUwEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=94b2d628\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2t4uwA5</a>"},{"pid":"f2b6b9fd6f5c2f93b22ff6f13444945157bb1915","tid":319328,"uid":37885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T05:47:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n從來都很喜歡蜘蛛俠，因為他夠平易近人，既沒有蝙蝠俠的雄厚家財，也<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有Iron Man的發明實力</span>。</blockquote><br />\n乜料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e348b47d40c6b6d7c29d007d34f4949ed9937161","tid":319328,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T05:49:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6182ee32702fc1aff835582217b9d750b55bc19","tid":319328,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T05:50:36.000Z","msg":"呢D垃圾影評究竟點寫得出"},{"pid":"018c0592ef183c183c38d47721896c87a143d246","tid":319328,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T05:53:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢D垃圾影評究竟點寫得出</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係邊個影評人<br />\n做咩唔出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92176249dcd53ed3cc22d3d8edfcd591b0c64e0","tid":319328,"uid":19265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T05:56:53.000Z","msg":"寫果個人究竟知唔知今集先係Marvel 同Sony合作？<br />\n之前都係Sony 自己做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3cfb85ee634ace4f832cf337e97233c500e59f","tid":319328,"uid":63233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T05:59:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df74f3908d016db0dc3511e69c39e06dbe8afb9c","tid":319328,"uid":63233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T05:59:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}